omen's roles and the devotional path.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aAsian Studies : Asian Literature. 4aAsian Studies : Asian Studies. 4aAsian Studies : India and South Asian Studies. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Hindu Studies. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Religion. 7aRELIGION / Hinduism / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438430898423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438430898/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles